  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: Now let us start the process of treating and feeding water. Special care
    has to be taken regarding the quality of the water being fed to the boiler. Hard
    water cannot be fed into the boiler, as it can lead to the formation of hard
    and adherent scales inside the boiler. These scales may cause localized overheating,
    increased fuel consumption, and bursting of water tubes. It is therefore necessary
    to treat the water before feeding it into the boiler.
