  m_text: "Let us now have a look at the normal shut down procedure of the boiler.
    Normal shutdown is followed as a regular shutdown method and under non-emergency
    conditions. \r\n1.Reduce the boiler load gradually to the minimum firing rate.
    This minimizes thermal stresses on boiler components and allows the system to
    stabilize.\r\n"
